General.Name: Victory Metals
General.Description: Victory Goldfields Limited engages in the exploration and development of gold projects in Australia. It holds interest in the Cue goldfields comprising 50 tenements with an area of approximately 7,520 hectares; and seven tenement applications, being the Victory Tenements, with an area of approximately 1,060 hectares located in Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Hughes Drilling Limited and changed its name to Victory Goldfields Limited in July 2021. Victory Goldfields Limited is based in Subiaco, Australia.
